{"tid":853404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左香港，仲有咩地方會咁怪","createTime":"2018-10-08T14:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T14:20:07.000Z","uid":124932,"like":68,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b294dbded94d353133914baa34af60d5686bfe","tid":853404,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"好多地方都會對自己政府不滿<br />\n但有咩地方係對外都會反自己政府，好似叫人制裁同取消香港關係法咁<br />\n<br />\n其實有呢個現象都幾可悲，其他地方就算圍內不滿自己政府，對外都會表現岀為國家驕傲之類<br />\n<br />\n但香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 想人地介入，但都唔代表幫到拖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9c02ab84ed13050f97818b8f33a665b2cea01c","tid":853404,"uid":15815,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"淪陷區"},{"pid":"3cde34143d511786310e8281ddbdba802be19838","tid":853404,"uid":23180,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"無軍力而市民抗爭又動輒入獄嘅殖民地<br />\n<br />\n只有外來人先有能力制裁對自己差嘅當權者"},{"pid":"0be3536feb3163cd641e4c0899a472147d959594","tid":853404,"uid":20867,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"除左香港，仲有咩地方會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住TVB </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743033d7312733266305704459a371d81ad0e3cd","tid":853404,"uid":198834,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"除咗香港，仲有邊個已發展地區係冇得自己選自己個政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25457a0a80b2d96f2f8d164f835d9401c4d3ce8d","tid":853404,"uid":121546,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"但係香港政府係under位